so uh just using these words in a slightly different way so friendship good friendship that's really all the people whom you know they compete from the intimate to just acquaintance really your friendship group your social friendship group yeah and um it's an encouragement if you have amongst that group people who are keen on the dharma yeah so so that's what you might say is an understanding of your friendship group yeah

